parts.text:
Slurm
```json
{
  "software": [
    "python",
    "pytorch",
    "slurm"
  ],
  "resources": {
    "nodes": 1,
    "time": "00:09:00",
    "partition": "small",
    "gpus": 1,
    "mail_type": "ALL",
    "mail_user": "sclaam@leeds.ac.uk"
  },
  "environment_variables": {
    "LD_LIBRARY_PATH": "set to the path of the python executable",
    "GOMPC_CPU_AFFINITY": "unset",
    "KMP_AFFINITY": "unset"
  },
  "script_arguments": [
    "model",
    "dataset",
    "num_workers",
    "RF_level",
    "type",
    "epochs",
    "name",
    "width",
    "record",
    "resume_solution"
  ],
  "additional_information": {
    "job_name": "pytorch_test",
    "error_file": "pytorch_test.err",
    "output_file": "pytorch_test.output"
  }
}
```
